name: Stencil Photo 5x7
description:
This is a print that is produced through B/W photographic methods. I designed the image and produced it in a darkroom myself. No two are the same. Each print is signed and numbered. This is a very limited edition. Only 16 were made and only 15 will be sold. 
Please understand that every print will not be pristine. Some may have minor flaws. Just consider it "character".
